  <brief_title>DP13 - A Phase II Study in Patients With Primary Aldosteronism</brief_title>
  <official_title>DP13 - A Phase II Study in Patients With Primary Aldosteronism to Evaluate the Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of DP13, Over an 8-week Treatment Period</official_title>
  <sponsors>
